      <title>马克龙对勒庞的严厉警告这次可能不起作用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/macron-s-dire-warnings-about-le-pen-may-not-work-this-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃马纽埃尔·马克龙在周三的新闻发布会上宣称，如果极右翼最终执政，经济将面临末日，他呼吁选民不要屈服于“极端狂热”。问题是，事实证明，这一历史悠久的策略越来越无效。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/macron-s-dire-warnings-about-le-pen-may-not-work-this-time</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 07:01:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>七国集团计划如何应对俄罗斯和中国日益增强的影响力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/g7-summit-russia-defense-spending-and-global-south-under-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国及其盟友寻求重新集结对乌克兰的援助，由中国和俄罗斯支持的新伙伴关系正变得更具影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/g7-summit-russia-defense-spending-and-global-south-under-focus</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 04:00:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿根廷抗议活动阴影下米莱改革即将通过</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/milei-s-signature-reforms-at-risk-in-tense-argentine-senate-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱签署的改革方案取得了关键胜利：在国会大楼前爆发暴力抗议活动后，参议院以微弱优势通过了米莱提出的综合法案，并以微弱优势初步批准了单独立法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/milei-s-signature-reforms-at-risk-in-tense-argentine-senate-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 15:57:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
